[APPLAUSE]

00:11:53.419 --> 00:11:55.210
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA:
Thank you, thank you.

00:11:55.210 --> 00:11:55.719
Thank you.

00:11:55.719 --> 00:11:57.510
I didn't know they were
