[EXHALES]

00:29:44.940 --> 00:29:46.215
Breathe in through the right.

00:29:46.215 --> 00:29:49.005
[INHALES]

00:29:52.430 --> 00:29:53.920
Breathe out through the left.

00:29:53.920 --> 00:29:57.392
[EXHALES]

00:30:00.870 --> 00:30:03.525
The last one, breathe
