00:30:38.190 --> 00:30:39.420
Come into the dhyana mudra.

00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:46.040
Eyes closed.

00:30:46.040 --> 00:30:51.440
Concentrating on the center of
your forehead, the ajna chakra.

00:30:59.630 --> 00:31:02.485
For all you Googlers, this
