It's out.

00:33:58.840 --> 00:34:05.280
[EXHALES IN SHORT BURSTS]
So that's the movement.

00:34:05.280 --> 00:34:06.490
Yeah?

00:34:06.490 --> 00:34:11.250
And you don't have to
move your entire body.

00:34:11.250 --> 00:34:15.150
It's only the breath and
your stomach that moves.

00:34:15.150 --> 00:34:19.590
So it's not-- no.

00:34:19.590 --> 00:34:21.739
Your body is upright.

00:34:21.739 --> 00:34:23.830
Align your chakras.

00:34:23.830 --> 00:34:25.839
You have to align
your back, straight.

00:34:29.449 --> 00:34:30.679
And we do it again.

00:34:30.679 --> 00:34:36.905
Everybody come into--
get your breath together.

