00:37:43.690 --> 00:37:44.898
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA: Lovely.

00:37:47.008 --> 00:37:47.994
[INAUDIBLE]

00:37:54.910 --> 00:37:56.770
First and foremost,
before you get

00:37:56.770 --> 00:37:58.160
down to doing the
Surya Namaskar,

00:37:58.160 --> 00:38:00.212
we have to do a stretch.

00:38:00.212 --> 00:38:03.000
Yoga is about action, reaction.

00:38:03.000 --> 00:38:07.240
So every stretch has
a counter-stretch.

00:38:07.240 --> 00:38:12.910
So before starting, just
loosen every part of your body.

00:38:12.910 --> 00:38:14.812
Just shake it all out.

00:38:14.812 --> 00:38:16.290
Yeah.

00:38:16.290 --> 00:38:17.960
Just shake it all out.

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:20.642
Hands.

00:38:20.642 --> 00:38:24.305
Yeah, just like-- just move.

00:38:24.305 --> 00:38:25.540
Yeah, just every part.

00:38:25.540 --> 00:38:26.530
It's like a dance.

00:38:26.530 --> 00:38:28.510
[LAUGHS] Yeah.

00:38:28.510 --> 00:38:35.060
Just-- just-- just
warm your body up.

00:38:35.060 --> 00:38:35.770
Yeah.

00:38:35.770 --> 00:38:36.895
Just kick your legs around.

00:38:45.160 --> 00:38:47.290
We'll just do the neck
rotation because it's

00:38:47.290 --> 00:38:49.190
very important to warm up.

00:38:49.190 --> 00:38:51.730
I cannot be more
emphasis on warm-ups.

00:38:55.270 --> 00:38:58.510
Never get into a regime
or an exercise routine

00:38:58.510 --> 00:39:00.280
without a warm-up.

00:39:00.280 --> 00:39:04.540
So you just look to
your right first.

00:39:08.460 --> 00:39:11.870
Center, slowly, to the left.

00:39:15.540 --> 00:39:18.970
Center, look straight up.

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:26.680
Try and go as behind as you can.

00:39:26.680 --> 00:39:28.960
Stretch your neck.

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:30.760
And you come down the same way.

00:39:30.760 --> 00:39:32.840
Try to touch your
chin to your chest.

00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:42.370
Right in the center,
straight ahead.

00:39:42.370 --> 00:39:43.480
Rotate your neck now.

00:39:50.920 --> 00:39:51.455
Three times.

00:39:54.256 --> 00:39:55.380
Looking towards your right.

00:39:59.690 --> 00:40:02.720
Come to the center.

00:40:02.720 --> 00:40:04.460
Three times on
the opposite side.

00:40:21.850 --> 00:40:27.150
And we go into Tadasana, OK,
where you stand like a tree.

00:40:27.150 --> 00:40:27.730
Hands up.

00:40:32.580 --> 00:40:35.130
Try and touch the skies.

00:40:35.130 --> 00:40:38.152
On your toes.

00:40:38.152 --> 00:40:38.985
Open out your chest.

00:40:41.855 --> 00:40:42.355
Breathe.

00:40:45.330 --> 00:40:46.660
Down.

00:40:46.660 --> 00:40:51.144
Hands on the side, come down.

00:40:51.144 --> 00:40:52.500
We do the same thing again.

00:40:55.710 --> 00:40:58.200
Go into Namaste right on top.

00:40:58.200 --> 00:40:58.700
Stretch.

00:41:02.107 --> 00:41:02.607
Stretch.

00:41:08.835 --> 00:41:09.335
Down.

00:41:11.890 --> 00:41:16.520
Try to touch your fingers
to the ground now.

00:41:16.520 --> 00:41:19.180
Breathe out.

00:41:19.180 --> 00:41:22.120
[EXHALES]

00:41:29.480 --> 00:41:30.050
Breathe in.

00:41:30.050 --> 00:41:30.640
Come up.

00:41:30.640 --> 00:41:34.105
[INHALES]

00:41:34.105 --> 00:41:37.080
[EXHALES]

00:41:37.080 --> 00:41:38.866
Can we do that again?

00:41:38.866 --> 00:41:40.740
And when you do it the
second time, trust me,

00:41:40.740 --> 00:41:43.370
you will go down lower.

00:41:43.370 --> 00:41:44.358
Hands up.

00:41:44.358 --> 00:41:45.762
[INHALES]

00:41:48.110 --> 00:41:48.990
Exhale.

00:41:48.990 --> 00:41:51.870
[EXHALES]

00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:00.090
Inhale.

00:42:00.090 --> 00:42:00.590
Come up.

00:42:00.590 --> 00:42:02.081
[INHALES]

00:42:04.070 --> 00:42:05.705
Hands on the side.

00:42:05.705 --> 00:42:06.205
Come down.

00:42:10.770 --> 00:42:12.446
We do the Surya Namaskar?

00:42:12.446 --> 00:42:13.300
GOPI KALLAYIL: Yeah.

00:42:13.300 --> 00:42:13.510
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA: Ready?

00:42:13.510 --> 00:42:13.952
[INAUDIBLE]

00:42:13.952 --> 00:42:15.278
GOPI KALLAYIL: They have
two, three, minutes, and then

00:42:15.278 --> 00:42:16.028
we're out of time.

00:42:16.028 --> 00:42:17.610
SHILPA SHETTY
KUNDRA: Oh, lovely.

00:42:17.610 --> 00:42:19.850
So only I'll be doing
the Surya Namaskar then.

00:42:19.850 --> 00:42:21.350
GOPI KALLAYIL: We'll
do it together.

00:42:21.350 --> 00:42:23.420
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA: Come,
let's do it together then.

00:42:23.420 --> 00:42:23.720
Yeah?

00:42:23.720 --> 00:42:24.511
GOPI KALLAYIL: Yes.

00:42:26.510 --> 00:42:29.010
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA: Make sure
that the breathing technique

00:42:29.010 --> 00:42:29.509
is right.

00:42:29.509 --> 00:42:32.340
So with every asana, breathe in.

00:42:36.140 --> 00:42:37.670
Breathe out.

00:42:37.670 --> 00:42:38.495
One leg behind.

00:42:43.620 --> 00:42:48.250
Chest, butt up, chest
to the floor first.

00:42:48.250 --> 00:42:50.244
And knees on the floor.

00:42:53.140 --> 00:42:55.360
Bhujangasana.

00:42:55.360 --> 00:42:57.400
Now you get into a Downward Dog.

00:42:57.400 --> 00:42:59.455
Make sure that the
heels touch the ground.

00:43:02.920 --> 00:43:06.920
Try to go towards your navel.

00:43:06.920 --> 00:43:08.370
One leg in front.

00:43:12.987 --> 00:43:13.570
Then the next.

00:43:17.170 --> 00:43:20.790
Come up slowly.

00:43:20.790 --> 00:43:21.390
Hands up.

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:25.020
Into Namaste.

00:43:27.590 --> 00:43:29.470
How did that make you feel?

00:43:29.470 --> 00:43:30.160
Awesome, right?

00:43:30.160 --> 00:43:32.241
Let's do that now in one go.

00:43:32.241 --> 00:43:32.740
Yeah?

00:43:32.740 --> 00:43:33.970
You got the technique.

00:43:33.970 --> 00:43:36.800
Ready?

00:43:36.800 --> 00:43:38.400
Hands up.

00:43:38.400 --> 00:43:40.506
Bend backwards.

00:43:40.506 --> 00:43:41.005
Down.

00:43:46.980 --> 00:43:47.735
Butt up.

00:43:47.735 --> 00:43:49.550
Only knees touch the floor.

00:43:55.390 --> 00:43:56.065
Downward Dog.

00:44:11.160 --> 00:44:12.330
Let's do three of these.

00:44:12.330 --> 00:44:15.000
One more, OK?

00:44:15.000 --> 00:44:17.510
Hands up.

00:44:17.510 --> 00:44:18.010
Down.

00:44:40.270 --> 00:44:42.820
That's fantastic.

00:44:42.820 --> 00:44:45.910
Make sure when you go
down, that position,

00:44:45.910 --> 00:44:48.480
I feel most people do it wrong.

00:44:48.480 --> 00:44:52.870
When you go down,
when you are here,

00:44:52.870 --> 00:44:54.970
make sure you go down like this.

00:44:54.970 --> 00:44:57.890
This is the right way to do it.

00:44:57.890 --> 00:45:01.470
Most people do this.

00:45:01.470 --> 00:45:03.040
That's not the right way.

00:45:03.040 --> 00:45:08.480
So only your-- this
is the way to do it.

00:45:08.480 --> 00:45:10.280
Then you come up.

00:45:10.280 --> 00:45:11.960
And then you go do this.

00:45:11.960 --> 00:45:17.900
In Downward Dog, try and always
concentrate and go backwards.

00:45:21.830 --> 00:45:22.840
I just showed it to you.

00:45:22.840 --> 00:45:27.830
When you guys do it, you
need to get this right.

00:45:27.830 --> 00:45:28.820
OK?

00:45:28.820 --> 00:45:31.321
We'll just do one more asana.

00:45:31.321 --> 00:45:35.060
We do the Virabhadrasana,
which is my favorite asana.

00:45:35.060 --> 00:45:37.311
It's great for the legs.

00:45:37.311 --> 00:45:37.810
OK?

00:45:42.320 --> 00:45:45.900
Feet hip width apart.

00:45:45.900 --> 00:45:47.360
Yeah?

00:45:47.360 --> 00:45:49.100
Lovely.

00:45:49.100 --> 00:45:50.570
Now, you turn one leg.

00:45:55.450 --> 00:45:56.440
Hands on the side.

00:45:59.120 --> 00:46:00.801
Hands on top.

00:46:00.801 --> 00:46:01.300
Bend.

00:46:06.680 --> 00:46:08.550
Breathe.

00:46:08.550 --> 00:46:11.960
You should feel the tension in
your glutes, on your thighs.

00:46:16.700 --> 00:46:17.542
Come up.

00:46:20.200 --> 00:46:21.500
Turn to the other side.

00:46:34.760 --> 00:46:37.090
Come up.

00:46:37.090 --> 00:46:38.690
Center.

00:46:38.690 --> 00:46:39.450
Hands on the side.

00:46:44.070 --> 00:46:46.120
Yay!

00:46:46.120 --> 00:46:46.810
That felt great.

00:46:46.810 --> 00:46:47.851
GOPI KALLAYIL: Beautiful.

00:46:47.851 --> 00:46:48.430
Thank you.

00:46:48.430 --> 00:46:49.763
SHILPA SHETTY KUNDRA: Thank you.

